headline: Energy Transition Today - Plexar Energy Advances Industrial Microgrid Solutions for Sustainability
summary: Copenhagen Infrastructure Partners and PensionDanmark have established Plexar Energy, a new company specializing in microgrids to advance the industrialization of renewable energy systems. This initiative seeks to capitalize on the increasing demand for microgrids, which promise faster electrification and energy independence for industries.
